beer.beer_description:
A deceptive golden glow of pale straw it looks like an innocent beer but don't let that fool you.

Your nasal hairs will be moshing along to the spice stone fruit aromas of our hops. From your first sniff you will know it isn't just another regular old Pale.

The deep rumble of complex spicy hop flavours doesn't hold back from a night's shredding. It's got a bit extra going on versus the  standard beer. At 5.6% ABV it leaves room for an unforgettable harmony of chords that don't just sound the same.
